dict.acceptation: 使发展；使发育；开发；培育；

sent.orig: Analysis purchasing status, work out purchasing strategy. Maintains and develop exist suppliers or develop new suppliers.
sent.trans: 分析采购状况，制定采购策略。维护与发展现有供应商的合作或开发新供应商。

sent.orig: Among conducting internal audit could develop integration audit, also could develop 3 system audits independently.
sent.trans: 其中内部审核实施时可以开展整合性审核，也可以独立开展三个体系的审核。

sent.orig: About 25% of patients who develop psoriasis go on to develop psoriatic arthritis.
sent.trans: 大约25％的银屑病患者会逐渐发展成银屑病关节炎。

sent.orig: Analysis purchasing status. Maintains and develop exist supplier or develop new supplier.
sent.trans: 分析采购状况，维护与发展现有供应商的合作，或开发新供应商。

sent.orig: Develop new market and customers. Develop new business and promote new products, extend market.
sent.trans: 开发新市场、新客户。发展新业务，推广新产品，努力拓展市场。
